      "role": "user",
      "content": "that balloon metaphor makes sense i guess. but it feels like there's something extra hidden in there. like, even when i check the math, the interest amount seems almost intentional, like it's designed to keep me stuck in this cycle for as long as possible. why does it feel like the math is working against me specifically?",
